        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "On November 2nd a Contest of Champions will be held in Lake Town. The contest will run the gamut of power ranges and signups will start on the 27th. Prizes will be awarded. Food and Drink of rare quality. fun and adventure await. And there will be one grand prize to be awarded to the bravest champion. All are welcome to Enter. Matches will be set up by the Guides. There will be a small entry fee of 50 gold per level."
          }
        }
