        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "As if that were not enough... These Servants of Sauron then assailed the Valley of Rivendell, many brave elven ranger and Ranger of the north were cut down. And Glorfindel was found unconscious among the dead. It is said that this all was masterminded by two very powerful Servants. Dylanth Pike and Ugah Boogah. It is rumored that Dylanth one of the most powerful wizards of the region has breached the protection of Rivendell. And there now stands a secret entrance that evil may pass through."
